                        <pre class="bg-dark text-light p-2 rounded small"><code># Run the configuration script
.\Configure-MCBDSVolumes.ps1

# The script will prompt you for:
# - Bedrock Server location (e.g., D:\MinecraftServer\bedrock)
# - Backup storage location (e.g., E:\Backups\minecraft)
# - Configuration files location (e.g., C:\MCBDSManager\config)

